-- First Australia API-5 OTC Thermal Coal Swap Trades, Argus Says
-- B y   B e n   S h a r p l e s
-- 2013-01-21T06:44:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-21/first-australia-api-5-otc-thermal-coal-swap-trades-argus-says.html
Deal based on the Australian API 5
index and was brokered by Marex Spectron, involving Standard
Bank as one of the counterparties, Argus said in an e-mailed
statement today  * API 5 represents heating value of 5,500 kilocalories a
kilogram, high ash coal
* NOTE: API 5 started in May 2012 by Argus and IHS McCloskey  To contact the reporter on this story:
